    <p>Conclusions</p>
    <p>Major consumers: display &amp; cell radio  WiFi power low in most situations</p>
    <p>CPU can be significant  Future power driver</p>
    <p>Where power is not going:  RAM  Audio  Bluetooth  Storage</p>
  </div>
